                            </div>
                            <figcaption>
                                <h3><a class="movtitle" href="/movie/dredd-2012-1080p/">Dredd</a></h3>
                                <p>The future America is an irradiated waste land. On its East Coast, running from
                                    Boston to Washington DC, lies Mega City One - a vast, violent metropolis where
                                    criminals rule the chaotic streets. The o...</p>
                            </figcaption>
                        </figure>
                        <span class="read_more"><a
                                    href="https://yifymovies.to/movie/dredd-2012-1080p/">Read More &raquo;</a></span>
                    </article>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>
{% endblock %}